name: Viking Women
overview: The Vikings changed Europe forever, yet half of them have almost completely disappeared from collective memory: the women.

episodes.name: Part 1: Sigrun's Wrath And The Discovery Of Iceland
episodes.overview: Viking women commanded ships and settled colonies. They took up arms and negotiated with emperors. Their traces can now be discovered all the way from America to Kiev. Without their biographies the period of the Vikings stays incomplete.  This is the story of Sigrun, in Norway, in the year 872.
